{"tid":1575483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[再光復屯門] 有人指控再光復令義士死不暝目","createTime":"2019-09-17T01:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T17:59:35.000Z","uid":102984,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ce74b406d8260f258d441d2f0c2b9edf99dae9","tid":1575483,"uid":102984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:19:39.000Z","msg":"話因為個遊行唔係focus主線。<br />\n<br />\n以下係條友響tg group到處share嘅&ldquo;文章&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n「921屯門遊行的建議」［請廣傳］<br />\n<br />\nfrom tg name: kyj hk democracy<br />\n<br />\n屯門遊行的主題應該是［五大訴求］，而不是［屯門公園大媽］。幾個月來，我們不惜犧牲、死傷慘重，追求的是［五大訴求］，而不是［屯門公園大媽］。<br />\n<br />\n即使［屯門公園大媽］完全解決，對［五大訴求］沒有任何幫助。我們必須對準政權，以［五大訴求］作為唯一議題，而不是［屯門公園大媽］，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">否則死去的手足將會死不瞑目、受傷/被捕的手足將會心如刀割</span></span>。手足拋頭顱、灑熱血，為的是［五大訴求］而不是［屯門公園大媽］。<br />\n<br />\n而家係關鍵時刻，抗爭焦點必須要集中［五大訴求］。如果Spin左去地區民生問題，政府和黑警最開心。如果遊行不是以［五大訴求］作為唯一議題，只會分散注意力，幫助政府維穩，可能仲衰過唔搞。<br />\n<br />\n誠意希望屯門遊行搞手能夠公開回應。遊行主題會不會改為［五大訴求］？而且不會牽涉［屯門公園大媽］？<br />\n<br />\n另外，921晚上7pm會有［921元朗站靜坐］，追究黑警責任，活動極度重要，我們必須廣泛在不同平台宣傳，務求幾十萬人迫爆元朗站，為政府帶來壓力。<br />\n<br />\n================================<br />\n<br />\n由於個指控實在太嚴重，所以我以關注組成員嘅身份響連登呢度開post俾所有人討論"},{"pid":"09fe040e70f36ca4d374293f78365893a49d299c","tid":1575483,"uid":8657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:20:49.000Z","msg":"我想你公開回應點令義士死不瞑目<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6165850ef258888713c1416e759ab2b7c28a23a","tid":1575483,"uid":256067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:21:20.000Z","msg":"我想你公開回應點令烈士死不瞑目"},{"pid":"48eadf2a491f0ad4cbf42758708d03b6e2d6a537","tid":1575483,"uid":256067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:22:17.000Z","msg":"出嚟啦喂 人哋幫你開埋po啦"},{"pid":"0c1a03076611bde86acc540c24e201b328c1b1d0","tid":1575483,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:22:40.000Z","msg":"我想你公開回應點令烈士死不瞑目<br />\n屌你老母，出黎呀"},{"pid":"e1ca631f9512b903e91f44ea7887be33bfdba59f","tid":1575483,"uid":140198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:22:44.000Z","msg":"我想你公開回應點令烈士死不瞑目<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8408b275a189c3c99c31f05c1009f91e20b805","tid":1575483,"uid":251651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aidDeKC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaidDeKC.jpg&h=4cd4a0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WQVmWXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWQVmWXY.jpg&h=53498910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個人係tg發表"},{"pid":"17a1f3c841e34d2686e342144f35ddd516793d4c","tid":1575483,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:29:24.000Z","msg":"佢要人公開回應，但又唔開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9d3bbfc2f5b08db2f2ba93bc5d2dafbba81ccc","tid":1575483,"uid":134214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"po都開埋 <br />\n唔夠膽入嚟屌？"},{"pid":"b9db008ddd52ab70dcf40b373607e9067b6938a2","tid":1575483,"uid":251651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:34:56.000Z","msg":"推，多啲人知發生咩事"},{"pid":"8b785982c4939647a41df259b93c6da174926895","tid":1575483,"uid":4796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:35:59.000Z","msg":"其他區都係以五大訴求為主題，民生議題就係副<br />\n屯門搞乜鳩"},{"pid":"1b0c95475ed0bd2de83465f35a14576e93483161","tid":1575483,"uid":1778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:36:18.000Z","msg":"幫推，當時人出來回應吧"},{"pid":"902cc7a108b8b0529802dd397a11f9902658bcb9","tid":1575483,"uid":128178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:38:00